data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. HAPPY NEW YEAR!  The seller has just installed a new 150 AMP top quality Cutler Hammer panel, install 2 8' ground rods and a new HVAC system.  Here's your chance to own a Manufactured Home on a residential lot YOU OWN! No HOA, rules, regulations, age limits and you can have your PETS.  This home has more space than you can image.  Open floor plan with Kitchen (Refrigerator, stove/oven, dishwasher included) dining room and open living room.  Currently has a salon room, office and a sewing room.  2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  Out back you have plenty of storage rooms, efficiency room and a 3pc bathroom.  There is a prep area with working sink, 1/2 bath next to laundry room with more storage, wood shed and tool & utility shed.  Dog area on side yard with a gate that leads out to the front/car port area.  The other side has a deck.  Updates include GFI outlets, deck painting and small needed repairs.
